{
  "info": {
    "name": "Axis Garage API — All Endpoints",
    "_postman_id": "axisgarage-api-complete-v1",
    "description": "Colección completa de la API REST de Axis Garage.\n\n**Flujo de uso:**\n1. Ejecuta 'Login (Admin)' → el JWT se guarda automáticamente en {{token}}\n2. Todos los endpoints protegidos usan el Bearer Token de la colección\n\n**Credenciales de prueba:**\n- ADMIN:   admin@axisgarage.com / admin123\n- MANAGER: manager@axisgarage.com / manager123\n- USER:    normal@axisgarage.com / user123",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      { "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (Admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('token', j.token); }",
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@axisgarage.com\",\n  \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/authenticate",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "authenticate"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Manager)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('token', j.token); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"manager@axisgarage.com\",\n  \"password\": \"manager123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/authenticate",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "authenticate"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (User)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('token', j.token); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"normal@axisgarage.com\",\n  \"password\": \"user123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/authenticate",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "authenticate"]
            }
          }
        },
